&lt;p&gt;Tower Research Capital is a leading quantitative trading firm founded in 1998. Tower has built its business on a high-performance platform and independent trading teams. We have a 25+ year track record of innovation and a reputation&amp;nbsp; for discovering unique market opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tower is home to some of the world’s best systematic trading and engineering talent. We empower portfolio managers to build their teams and strategies independently while providing the economies of scale that come from a large, global organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
